466
00:20:20,916 --> 00:20:25,458
[MINORU gasps]
Huh, what, who me? Huh?

467
00:20:25,541 --> 00:20:26,875
You want me?

468
00:20:26,958 --> 00:20:30,541
Akira-sama? Me?
Oh, okay, got it.

469
00:20:30,625 --> 00:20:36,416
Hey, um. I think we're
on the air right now so uh...

470
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:39,083
if I don't do somethin' now
they're gonna change--

471
00:20:39,166 --> 00:20:40,875
[music playing]

472
00:20:40,958 --> 00:20:44,666
Hiya, Luckies! Or you know,
however she says that line.

473
00:20:44,750 --> 00:20:47,541
Okay, guys, Lucky Channel's
on the air again this week

474
00:20:47,625 --> 00:20:49,791
and I'm Minoru Shiraishi,
the assistant.

475
00:20:49,875 --> 00:20:50,916
Akira-sama's in a bad mood.

476
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:54,208
Ha!

477
00:20:54,291 --> 00:20:57,416
How dare you introduce
yourself before introducing me,

478
00:20:57,500 --> 00:21:01,208
Akira Kogami. Do you not
understand what rank is?

479
00:21:01,291 --> 00:21:02,208
No, I was--

480
00:21:02,291 --> 00:21:04,166
--[thuds]
--Huh!

481
00:21:04,250 --> 00:21:05,708
I've noticed you've
been getting quite

482
00:21:05,791 --> 00:21:07,791
popular around here lately,

483
00:21:07,875 --> 00:21:09,666
you and those pigtails.

484
00:21:09,750 --> 00:21:11,375
Me? Popular? No not at all.

485
00:21:11,458 --> 00:21:13,083
You're so full
of yourself, it makes me sick!

486
00:21:13,166 --> 00:21:14,791
I'm terribly sorry!

487
00:21:14,875 --> 00:21:16,375
First off, everybody
was expecting

488
00:21:16,458 --> 00:21:18,041
the Akira fashion project

489
00:21:18,125 --> 00:21:20,416
to showcase me,
yes, me and my pigtails.

490
00:21:20,500 --> 00:21:22,000
What are those?

491
00:21:22,083 --> 00:21:24,125
You're right,
you're absolutely right!

492
00:21:24,208 --> 00:21:26,625
Hmm, I'm gonna
wear twin drills.

493
00:21:26,708 --> 00:21:28,708
You're kidding, twin drills?

494
00:21:28,791 --> 00:21:30,833
Don't underestimate
the speed of the getter.

495
00:21:30,916 --> 00:21:33,708
[scoffs] Number two, huh?
Pigtails are over.

496
00:21:33,791 --> 00:21:36,083
The next big thing is
going to be twin drills.

497
00:21:36,166 --> 00:21:37,958
Didn't Konata say in episode two

498
00:21:38,041 --> 00:21:40,000
that a drill is kinda
like a guy's, you know?

499
00:21:40,083 --> 00:21:41,833
Did she now?

500
00:21:41,916 --> 00:21:43,750
All righty, everyone, we're
gonna straighten this out

501
00:21:43,833 --> 00:21:45,541
on our radio show
and on our website!

502
00:21:45,625 --> 00:21:48,000
So, until the next episode.

503
00:21:48,083 --> 00:21:51,500
Bye, me!

504
00:21:51,583 --> 00:21:52,500
--[AKIRA] So...
--[MINORU] Yes.

505
00:21:52,583 --> 00:21:53,791
[AKIRA]
The pigtails.

506
00:21:53,875 --> 00:21:54,916
[MINORU]
Oh, the ones I had.

507
00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:56,625
[AKIRA]
The ones in the picture.

508
00:21:56,708 --> 00:21:58,041
[MINORU]
Yes.

509
00:21:58,125 --> 00:21:59,791
--[AKIRA] Were those sunflowers?
--[MINORU] They were.

510
00:21:59,875 --> 00:22:01,458
[AKIRA] I think I've
seen those somewhere before.

511
00:22:01,541 --> 00:22:02,875
[MINORU]
What do you mean?

512
00:22:02,958 --> 00:22:04,583
--[AKIRA] Years ago...
--[MINORU] Whoa! Hang on a sec!

513
00:22:04,666 --> 00:22:06,541
--[AKIRA] One of my first--
--[MINORU] Gero gero! Gero gero!

514
00:22:08,500 --> 00:22:10,708
[TSUKASA]
Boy, was I nervous.

515
00:22:10,791 --> 00:22:13,208
[MIYUKI] It was very cute
and very well done.

516
00:22:13,291 --> 00:22:15,416
[TSUKASA] Don't you get nervous
on the first song you sing?

517
00:22:15,500 --> 00:22:18,666
You think "am I gonna sing this
song good enough," you know?

518
00:22:18,750 --> 00:22:20,416
[KAGAMI]
Your turn, Miyuki!

519
00:22:20,500 --> 00:22:23,083
[KONATA] I'd like her
to sing "Omoide Ga Ippai."

520
00:22:23,166 --> 00:22:24,625
[KAGAMI]
Why that one?

521
00:22:24,708 --> 00:22:26,458
[MIYUKI] Would you please
hand me the mic?

522
00:22:26,541 --> 00:22:28,250
[TSUKASA]
Here. Good luck!

523
00:22:28,333 --> 00:22:30,583
[MIYUKI] Umm, I don't
do this very often,

524
00:22:30,666 --> 00:22:32,708
so I'd like
to apologize ahead of time

525
00:22:32,791 --> 00:22:34,291
if my singing hurts your ears.

526
00:22:34,375 --> 00:22:35,750
[KAGAMI]
Don't worry, you'll do great!

527
00:22:39,708 --> 00:22:42,000
[KAGAMI]
Wow, good one!

528
00:22:42,083 --> 00:22:46,250
[KONATA] I totally get the
connection here. Nice, Miyuki.

529
00:22:50,208 --> 00:22:53,125
[MIYUKI sings in Japanese]

530
00:22:53,208 --> 00:22:55,875
[KONATA]
Oh, her voice is awesome!

531
00:22:55,958 --> 00:22:58,708
This is a new kind of moe
and it's workin'.

532
00:22:58,791 --> 00:23:01,000
[TSUKASA]
Yuki-chan, you're so cool!

533
00:23:01,083 --> 00:23:04,625
[MIYUKI sings in Japanese]

534
00:23:37,833 --> 00:23:40,000
[ANNOUNCER] On the next episode
of "Lucky Star"...

535
00:23:40,083 --> 00:23:42,333
Tsukasa here!
Wait, time's up?

536
00:23:42,416 --> 00:23:44,833
Next time "Energetic
Despite Not Being Myself."

537
00:23:44,916 --> 00:23:46,250
[ANNOUNCER]
Look forward to it!

